pan class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ylq1665702607548.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ylq1665702607548.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ylq1665702607548.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ylq1665702607548\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__clrmess_211915\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Clear all text from the message frame and message line.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__topic_d70157e1_d70158e1_d70159e1\">\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__p_d70160e1_d70161e1_d70162e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__codeblock_b5l_jwz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">clrmess</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__topic_d46017e1_d46018e1_d46019e1_d46020e1_d46021e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d763614e65\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__topic_d46022e1_d46023e1_d46024e1_d46025e1_d46026e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d763614e74\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__topic_d46027e1_d46028e1_d46029e1_d46030e1_d46031e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d763614e83\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__p_d70178e1_d70179e1_d70180e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span> statement clears all text from the message frame. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">store</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">erase</span> statements also clear the message frame.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ylq1665702607548__note_w1432ab1b7b9b5_w1433ab1b7b9_w1434ab1b7_w1435ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> In the\n            Debugger, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span> is disabled by default.\n         </div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the use of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clrmess</span> statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n clrmess\n putmess \"Form %%$formname loaded at %%$time.\"\n edit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afo1665702607468.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Askmess</a><p>Specify whether the message is displayed as an askmess message.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubi1665702607312.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>message</a><p>Display the specified string in the message line (if it is available), or an interactive dialog box.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubo1665702607631.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>putmess</a><p>Append text to the message frame.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/blc1719554861507.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$putmess</a><p>Send a message to the message frame, or return the contents of the message frame.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534142\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534142\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "clrmess Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Clear all text from the message frame and message line. clrmess Copy Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description The clrmess statement clears all text from the message frame. The store and erase statements also clear the message frame. Note: In the Debugger, clrmess is disabled by default. The following example shows the use of the clrmess statement: operation exec clrmess putmess \"Form %%$formname loaded at %%$time.\" edit end; exec Copy Related Links Askmess Specify whether the message is displayed as an askmess message. message Display the specified string in the message line (if it is available), or an interactive dialog box. putmess Append text to the message frame. $putmess Send a message to the message frame, or return the contents of the message frame. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}